name: Columbina (Genshin Impact) - Realistic + Semi-realistic + Anime - LoRA
description:
Columbina (Genshin Impact) - Realistic + Semi-realistic + Anime - LoRA

Making models is costing me my children's tuition. Do you like what I do? Feel free to buy me a coffee 🤗💖

This LoRA was made due to the request of an Anon Discord user and my personal love for the Character of Columbina or Damselette, the 3rd of the Fatui Harbingers. I used NED (Never Ending Dream) as a base model for training. This LoRA was trained on about 70 Images of Columbina since they're aren't that many images of her. I tried either way and it turned out well so I hope you like it.

It's flexible enough to make her in any style (realistic or anime, with a bit of help from style loras for a more dramatic effect) and a few outfits and hairstyle. Please check the examples.

Please be aware that while the LoRA itself is quite flexible with various weights. The Iconic Mask of Columbina will not always work or has a very low chance of working on models other than NED itself.

There isn't any trigger words that specially trigger the LoRA ( I don't know how to do that ) but the LoRA works just fine at a weight of "0.9" but might require tuning based on the model you're using it on. Works great on NeverEnding Dream and with Korean/Japanese likeness loras, or on any anime model out there.

Please enjoy and consider supporting me.

How to use LoRA's in auto1111:

  • Update webui (use git pull like here or redownload it)

  • Copy the file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Select your LoRA like in this video

  • Make sure to change the weight according to the instructions (by default it's :1)
